Comment: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Comment: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.55,orig,,0,0,0,,I don't have any more magic.
Comment: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:46.35,orig,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you... or the others.
Comment: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:14.50,orig,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.50,orig,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, I'm sorry, Shihoru.
Comment: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:56.10,orig,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to make you talk about all that.
Comment: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.20,orig,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.56,orig,,0,0,0,,Ranta apologized! I wonder if it'll rain tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:05.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Wait, no. It might snow tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.65,orig,,0,0,0,,Before we do...
Comment: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.30,orig,,0,0,0,,Merry, I want to talk to you.
Comment: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.00,orig,,0,0,0,,...for a parting.
Comment: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:33.35,orig,,0,0,0,,We used to have a Priest named Manato in our party.
Comment: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:51.10,orig,,0,0,0,,We used to have a Priest named Manato in our party.
Comment: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:19.80,orig,,0,0,0,,And Manato got us together and made us into a party.
Comment: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:15.00,orig,,0,0,0,,And I, uh, I do feel kinda bad about\Nmaking a big deal when I get a small cut.
Comment: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.23,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:04.70,orig,,0,0,0,,Then, do you want to have dinner with us?
Comment: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:19.75,orig,,0,0,0,,Hey little goblin slayers! You heading to Damuro today, too?
Comment: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:31.71,orig,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:29.45,orig,,0,0,0,,Once in a blue moon, there are moments\Nwhen I automatically know exactly where to hit.
Comment: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:51.15,orig,,0,0,0,,Manato, I'm not worried or overexcited or anything.

Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heal Michiki, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry, hurry! Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hayashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.65,fix,,0,0,0,,I've used up all my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.65,fix,,0,0,0,,No! I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Please, Hayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:46.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:48.90,Alt,,0,0,0,,...or the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2500)}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember how we got back above ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe my body remembered the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinohara took us in, and we\Njoined Orion, but Merry left soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was painful for her to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't say that, but I could see it in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When she saw me, she saw a past she couldn't regain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't help seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Merry moved from\Nparty to party, never staying long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,From what other people say about her,\Nshe isn't the same as she used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I brought Merry back above ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if that's... really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, she's an empty shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She might have... left herself down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand the pain of losing a comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've experienced it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not forget that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You will move forward while holding on to that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please treasure the comrades you have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they are gone, they will not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, you don't realize this... until afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:11.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:16.25,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:31.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:34.55,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:40.90,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:50.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:54.70,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:04:00.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:07.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:13.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:21.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, that was completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What was useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we know her past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have anything to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be nice to her just\Nbecause she's had a rough past?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,That's what you're saying, Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she any different from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying we haven't had a rough past?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all our fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to be okay being friends\Nwith someone who won't treat us as friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think... anyone here... was unaffected...\Nwhen we lost Manato-kun... everybody was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But to make up for it, I think we should try to be nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if we could... and if she could, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta, you said that she's no different from us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we don't try to get to know her,\Nshe won't try to get to know us either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't treat Merry as a friend,\Nshe won't treat us as her friends either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you trying to get to know {\i1}me{\i1}, Haruhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you guys always ignoring my thoughts and opinions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Ranta, you always say unnecessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you {\i1}only{\i0} say unnecessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when you call me flat-chested, it hurts my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's those things that are unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mo-Moguzo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Is that how you've been feeling, Ranta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:08.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's not only Merry that I haven't been paying attention to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:14.85,fix,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be more careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because I think of you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then you better be careful, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with ailing an idiot, "idiot"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At least give me time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You? {\i1}Think{\i0} about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we'll be seeing her tomorrow,\Nso I need to think about how to face her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:46.95,fix,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.50,fix,,0,0,0,,You know, Shihoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.15,fix,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:56.15,fix,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to make you talk about all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.20,fix,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.80,fix,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it'll rain tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,You say useless things, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:02.60,fix,,0,0,0,,No, wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.00,fix,,0,0,0,,It might snow tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think that sounds like the right saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how all of us will face Merry tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just saying that it's actually raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.05,fix,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun, that dagger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one I dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been myself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We might find their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't any goblins that were good targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain doesn't help either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.70,fix,,0,0,0,,But before that, Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.35,fix,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you say anything, if you want\Nme to leave the party, just say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Merry, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it we've been acting strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:05.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,After hearing her story yesterday,\Nwe don't know how to treat her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:08.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:15.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Merry felt that something was off\Nand probably prepared herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.05,fix_it,,0,0,0,,For example, for a parting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:19.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,For an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry, I want to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.05,fix,,0,0,0,,We used to have a Priest in our party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.35,fix,,0,0,0,,His name was {Robert Paulson}Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:48.45,fix,,0,0,0,,We used to have a Priest in our party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.20,fix,,0,0,0,,His name was Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably more accurate to say we let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato healed us, even when we only had scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He and Moguzo were also our shields during battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was also our leader,\Nso he was basically doing three jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But before we knew it, we took that for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was easy for Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't show it on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even try to imagine how he was feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, all I can do is imagine how he was feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato is dead, so he's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When Manato died, I seriously thought that was it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we want to keep living, we can't just do nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I asked you to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we can't do anything without a Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't any other reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, we were originally just\Nthe ones left over that nobody picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.30,fix,,0,0,0,,And Manato got us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.90,fix,,0,0,0,,And made us into a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in the same party,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be times when things don't go smoothly,\Nwhen you get angry, and when you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, they really are your precious friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter why you became friends,\Nbut that you are friends at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also think of you as a friend, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I also think of you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. And you're super cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's reassuring to have you here, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.40,fix,,0,0,0,,And I, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:14.95,fix,,0,0,0,,I do feel kinda bad about making\Na big deal when I get a small cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's about to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Ranta is apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That joke's getting old!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, if you want... you want to come\Nwith us to get Moguzo a helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.40,fix,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Then, if it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.80,fix,,0,0,0,,...do you want to have dinner with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you keep living, a new day will come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we found a cute helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And we somehow had enough money, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta didn't pitch in even one copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That discount I got was what I paid, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:15:01.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Because of Ranta's aggressive haggling, we got\Nthe price down from forty-two to eighteen silvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:49.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,I feel like maybe we're slowly\Ngetting a little closer to Merry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:56.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,And once, everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,...we always go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, goblin slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going, goblin slayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:19.75,fix,,0,0,0,,You heading to Damuro today, too, little goblin slayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably gonna hunt all\Nthe goblins outta this place soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Those idiots need to shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't respond to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This soup is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try making it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriosly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're okay with something similar, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:45.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Day after day, it's goblins, goblins, goblins, goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:52.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Rain or shine, it's goblins, goblins,\Ngoblins, goblins, goblins, goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:17:00.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,At first, they all looked the same, but\Nrecently, I've been able to tell them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:04.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,There are many males and few females.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:12.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,According to Merry, most of the females are in\NDamuro's new city, surrounded by high level males.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not jealous of that harem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the female goblins would fall for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those that don't understand my charm are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand it, you know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry, who would you choose from the three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:31.70,fix,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is there to be shy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:04.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,I really haven't seen Merry smile before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,We make sure to have nutritious meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,And it's fine to stay in the rundown\NVolunteer Soldier housing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Even if we had the money to stay in nicer\Nplaces, we should use that for equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,I especially want to invest in Moguzo's armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:27.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,We definitely can't afford anything\Ncustom made with sheet metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:32.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,Instead, we bought a more affordable\Nused one and had a blacksmith fit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:37.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Even so, the pieces all cost a couple silvers or more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Then there are skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:45.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,I learned Sneaking and Swat to mute my footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:50.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shihoru's Sleepy Shadow is shadow\Nmagic that puts enemies to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhaust!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:55.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,...is a skill that immediately creates\Ndistance between you and the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:01.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ranta just likes shouting out his skill names.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:05.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Moguzo's War Cry paralyzes the enemy for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:11.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yume learned Swift, raising her bow accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:15.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,With Mouse Hole, she can also\Nquickly dodge an enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:23.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Merry's always been levels above us,\Nso it's reassuring to have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:29.45,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Once in a while, there are moments when\NI automatically know exactly where to hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:36.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,My blade easily slips through,\Nand it's tip touches something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,As it touches, I know I've hit the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Before I realize it, I've already pierced through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:48.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,I actually have no idea what this light is either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Teacher Barbara next time I see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time, Haruhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:19:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of like how you can't sleep the night before a field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.80,fix,,0,0,0,,Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.30,fix,,0,0,0,,...I'm not worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.20,fix,,0,0,0,,...or overexcited or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,How many days have we been in Grimgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't remember when I stopped counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:22.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's one thing for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:29.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Wherever we came from, we're all friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:34.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,And we're definitely living our lives together here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show you what our party is like now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:23.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,When I try touching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:29.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,the dry air after a rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:36.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,like a sprouting flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:42.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,fragments of memories overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:55.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The warmth you gave this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:23:03.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,led me to a future I can treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:13.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I chased your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:19.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder when you became so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:26.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will probably find what I searched the vast world for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:33.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,at the end of this journey.
